  "title": "fix(pr): Testing PR on master",
  "body": "The script to validate PRs was really confusing about what being a PR\nmeant or not. This version should work better.\n\nBasically it will succeed when not on Travis, reject PRs not on\ndevelop, except if they are on master with either a `docs()` or\na `hotfix` mention.\n\nSo this very own PR, even if done on master, should just be valid and fix #931\n",
